The package libcln can be used via CMake:

    find_library(cln CONFIG REQUIRED)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE cln::cln)

The package libcln can be imported via CMake FindPkgConfig module:

    find_package(PkgConfig)
    PKG_CHECK_MODULES(CLN)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE PkgConfig::CLN)

And the package provide a executable `pi`:

    the path of executable: <package_dir>/tools/libcln/pi
